code: @Override public AcknowledgedResponse newResponse() {     return new AcknowledgedResponse(). }
public void setAllowNoForecasts(boolean allowNoForecasts) {     this.allowNoForecasts = allowNoForecasts. }
@Override public void readFrom(StreamInput in) throws IOException {     super.readFrom(in).     jobId = in.readString().     forecastId = in.readString().     allowNoForecasts = in.readBoolean(). }
@Override public void writeTo(StreamOutput out) throws IOException {     super.writeTo(out).     out.writeString(jobId).     out.writeString(forecastId).     out.writeBoolean(allowNoForecasts). }
